Reasoning: The paper discusses automated methods based on computer vision and deep learning for analyzing visual content data, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the usage of these methods in political analysis, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), multimedia (cs.MM), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as well. However, given the focus on visual content analysis, cs.CV is the most likely category.
